<br>
The formula for the mana portion of both Wind of Marr and Chorus of Marr is 8 + 1/6 Level rounded down<br>
<br>
70/6 = 11.66 (11)<br>
<br>
11 + 8 = 19<br>
<br>
I verified it on test server, and both songs are doing 19/tick.<br>
<br>
